# Knowledge Sync - Test Prompts
# These prompts test the knowledge sync workflow between JIRA and Confluence

## Prompt 1: Resolved Issues Query
User: List the JIRA issues resolved this week
Expected Behavior: Should query JIRA for recently resolved issues with summaries

## Prompt 2: Release Notes Search
User: Find the current release notes page in Confluence
Expected Behavior: Should locate the release notes page for the current version

## Prompt 3: Content Update
User: Add the resolved issues to the release notes in Confluence
Expected Behavior: Should update Confluence page with formatted issue summaries

## Prompt 4: Verification
User: Verify the release notes match the resolved JIRA issues
Expected Behavior: Should cross-reference Confluence content with JIRA data
